  "prompt": "An artistic conceptual illustration showing a single individual standing within a chaotic crowd, such as a football stadium or carnival street. The crowd is expressive, loud, and emotional — people are shouting, dancing, waving arms, lost in celebration. In contrast, the central figure is calm, still, and inwardly focused, with sharper, clearer lines, and a subtle glow. The crowd around is drawn in blurred, exaggerated motion and vibrant colors, while the individual is in cooler, serene tones. The image symbolizes loss of self in the group versus inner awareness and self-remembering."
}

